import numpy as np

def generate_primes(n):
    is_prime = np.ones((n,), dtype=bool)
    is_prime[:2] = 1
    N_max = int(np.sqrt(len(is_prime))) + 1
    for j in range(2, N_max):
        is_prime[j * j::j] = False
    return np.nonzero(is_prime)[0]
